{"thag6.10:0.1":"Theragatha 6.10 ","thag6.10:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thag6.10:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag6.10:0.4":"Sumanattheragatha ","thag6.10:1.1":"“Yada navo pabbajito, ","thag6.10:1.2":"jatiya sattavassiko; ","thag6.10:1.3":"Iddhiya abhibhotvana, ","thag6.10:1.4":"pannagindam mahiddhikam. ","thag6.10:2.1":"Upajjhayassa udakam, ","thag6.10:2.2":"anotatta mahasara; ","thag6.10:2.3":"Aharami tato disva, ","thag6.10:2.4":"mam sattha etadabravi”. ","thag6.10:3.1":"“Sariputta imam passa, ","thag6.10:3.2":"agacchantam kumarakam; ","thag6.10:3.3":"Udakakumbhamadaya, ","thag6.10:3.4":"ajjhattam susamahitam. ","thag6.10:4.1":"Pasadikena vattena, ","thag6.10:4.2":"kalyanairiyapatho; ","thag6.10:4.3":"Samaneronuruddhassa, ","thag6.10:4.4":"iddhiya ca visarado. ","thag6.10:5.1":"Ajaniyena ajanno, ","thag6.10:5.2":"sadhuna sadhukarito; ","thag6.10:5.3":"Vinito anuruddhena, ","thag6.10:5.4":"katakiccena sikkhito. ","thag6.10:6.1":"So patva paramam santim, ","thag6.10:6.2":"sacchikatva akuppatam; ","thag6.10:6.3":"Samanero sa sumano, ","thag6.10:6.4":"ma mam jannati icchati”ti. ","thag6.10:6.5":"… Sumano thero …. "}